Run install-gae-sdk.sh in order to install appengine-local-runtime (not included in Maven repository).
Run mvn clean install to compile the application.
Run run-gae.sh to run the application locally. You will need to download the SDK and unpack it on your own computer at this stage.
Create a new AppEngine application (http://appengine.google.com/).
Modify ./gaedownload-appengine/src/main/webapp/WEB-INF/appengine-web.xml and put in name and version number of your application.
Run deploy-gae.sh to deploy the application.

